<div type="translation">
<head>Translation</head>
<p>The platform is the property of Chrysanthos the son of Diogenes the son of Diogenes the son of (Attalos, the son of Attalos the son of) Attalos the son of Apollonios the son of Perigenes Chrysanthos, and of his children and grandchildren and whomever he himself may wish.</p>
</div>
